@database key.guide
@title "PGP Key"
@wordwrap
@node MAIN "My PGP public key"
@{b}My PGP Public Key@{ub}

This is my PGP public key.  @{"Click here" system "pgp-script"} to add this key to your public key
ring.

@{b}NOTES@{ub}

For the above script to work, all the following must be TRUE:

1) PGP must already have been installed.
2) The assign "PGP:" must be assigned to the directory containing PGP.
3) The PGP program itself must be in either "PGP:" or "PGP:bin"
4) The script run by the above link is experimental and may not work on
   all systems.


