The above key is also available from any of the public key servers.  See
the document "keyserv.doc" that comes with PGP for details of these servers
and how to extract keys.

If you have trouble with the key servers you can also obtain the key
directly by e-mail from @{"me" link contact.guide/MAIN}.

@endnode

